metadata.name: ANITA
metadata.description: Anita is an angel-eared goddess who stands completely still in the earth's atmosphere. Anita, representing justice, is the first goddess to live in the earth's atmosphere. She rules the voices according to hers justice. According to this legend, Anita appeals to all the hearts that beat for evil in the world when they are at their weakest. This call leaves them alone with their conscience. All hearts that don't listen are doomed to decay and die.
